<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM5.9.8">
<l>ampoṉā rulaka mēḻu maṟiyavāyp pāṭi taṉṉuḷ</l>
<l>kompaṉār piṉṉai kōlaṅ kūṭutaṟ kēṟu koṉṟāṉ</l>
<l>cempoṉār matiḷkaḷ cūḻnta teṉtirup pēruḷ mēvum</l>
<l>empirāṉ nāmam nāḷu mēttinā ṉuynta vāṟē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The way I was saved was by daily praising the name of the one</l>
<l>Who killed the bulls to embrace the beauty of Piṉṉai,</l>
<l rend="indent">the creeper-like lady,</l>
<l>In the herder hamlet, so that [those of] the seven,</l>
<l rend="indent">beautiful golden worlds would see,</l>
<l>Our lord, who dwells in Tiruppēr of the South surrounded by walls</l>
<l rend="indent">covered with rose gold.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
